<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>YIP-26</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/feather-icons"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    h3,
    h4 {
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }

      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .animate-slideUp {
      animation: slideUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    }
  </style>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/home.css" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@3.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="m-0 p-0 overflow-x-hidden">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 z-50 flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-[#0b1324] shadow w-full">
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->

  <section id="home" class="hero">
    <div class="hero__bg" role="img" aria-label="YIP background image"></div>
    <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero__content">
      <h1 class="hero_title text-6xl">Young Innovators Program</h1>
      <h2 class="hero_subtitle">7th Edition</h2>
      <div class="hero__cta">
        <a class="btn btn--light bg-blue-600 text-white" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Registration will begin soon</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="about py-10">
    <div class="about_container max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 w-full">
      <div class="about_grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="about_content">
          <p class="section_subheader">About Us</p>
          <h3 class="section_header">Event History</h3>
          <p class="para">
            The Young Innovators Program serves as a distinguished platform
            dedicated to fostering the scientific curiosity and
            problem-solving acumen of aspiring young minds.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p class="para">
            <strong>Eligibility Criteria:</strong>
            This competition exclusively welcomes students currently enrolled
            in grades VIII to XII, with the explicit objective of
            acknowledging and nurturing their creative potential. We implore
            you not to allow your exceptional ideas to languish in dormancy.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p class="para">
            Top teams nationwide will be selected after the first round and
            they will be called to Indian Institute of Technology, Kharagpur
            to exhibit and demonstrate their models or prototype and charts
            which will be evaluated by professors of IIT Kharagpur.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6 my-auto">
          <!-- Item 1 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 p-4 rounded-lg animate-slideUp">
            <!-- Icon -->
            <span class="shrink-0 text-blue-500 text-3xl">
              <i class="ri-global-fill"></i> <!-- Remix icon -->
            </span>
            <!-- Text -->
            <p class="text-sm md:text-lg font-medium">
              Present projects to esteemed researchers and guests.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 p-4 rounded-lg animate-slideUp">
            <span class="shrink-0 text-blue-500 text-3xl">
              <i class="ri-bar-chart-fill"></i>
            </span>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-lg font-medium">
              Immerse in IIT Kharagpur's scientific environment.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 3 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 p-4 rounded-lg animate-slideUp">
            <span class="shrink-0 text-blue-500 text-3xl">
              <i class="ri-thumb-up-fill"></i>
            </span>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-lg font-medium">
              Join 7<sup>th</sup> YIP and shine.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>



      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="timeline" class="section section--darkimage">
    <div class="section-bg" role="img" aria-label="Timeline background"></div>
    <div class="section-dim"></div>

    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title">Event Timeline</h2>
      <div class="section__line"></div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <article class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="tl-content">
            <h3 class="tl-title">Registration</h3>
            <p>
              The principal needs to nominate a coordinating teacher for this
              program, who will be given a user ID and password for
              registration of the students. The students need to form a team
              of 2-3 members and submit their name and details to the
              coordinating teacher of the school.
            </p>
            <span class="tl-chip">Registration will start soon</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="tl-content">
            <h3 class="tl-title">Round 1</h3>
            <p>
              Round I Submission Starts The team will submit their abstract of
              the project ideas briefing the scientific proposal based on the
              chosen theme. The online submissions of the projects will be
              done by the coordinating teacher by using his/her user id and
              password on the portal. Round 1 results will be released on our
              website. All participants who make it to the next round will
              also receive the news via email. The selected students will
              proceed to round 2.
            </p>
            <span class="tl-chip">To be announced </span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="tl-content">
            <h3 class="tl-title">Round 2 (Semifinal) @ IIT Kharagpur</h3>
            <p>
              Top teams nationwide will be selected after the first round and
              they will be called to Indian Institute of Technology, Kharagpur
              to exhibit and demonstrate their models or prototype and charts
              which will be evaluated by professors of IIT Kharagpur. The
              selected team need to confirm their presence for a two-day event
              held at IIT Kharagpur. The registration fees for this round will
              be declared after the announcement of the results of the 1st
              round.Selected teams exhibit and demonstrate prototypes at IIT
              Kharagpur.
            </p>
            <span class="tl-chip">To be announced </span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="tl-content">
            <h3 class="tl-title">Round 3 (Final) @ IIT Kharagpur</h3>
            <p>
              The qualifying teams from the second round will be qualified for
              the winners round. In this round each team will be given an
              opportunity to demonstrate their ideas in the form of a
              presentation followed by a Q&A session.
            </p>
            <span class="tl-chip">To be announced </span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery -->
  <section class="w-full" id="gallery">
    <h1 class="text-center my-4 text-3xl font-semibold">
      Gallery
    </h1>

    <div class="relative bg-yellow-900 
           md:w-[700px] md:h-[400px] 
           w-[90%] h-[250px] 
           mx-auto overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-lg" id="slider">

      <!-- Slides -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide active">
        <img src="images/gallery_1.jpg" alt="Gallery 1" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide">
        <img src="images/gallery_2.jpg" alt="Gallery 2" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide">
        <img src="images/gallery_3.jpg" alt="Gallery 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide">
        <img src="images/gallery_4.jpg" alt="Gallery 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide">
        <img src="images/gallery_5.jpg" alt="Gallery 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide">
        <img src="images/gallery_6.jpg" alt="Gallery 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide">
        <img src="images/IMG_4443.JPG" alt="Gallery 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" />
      </div>

      <!-- Buttons -->
      <button class="absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 left-2 
             bg-black/50 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-full 
             hover:bg-black/70 transition z-10" onclick="changeSlide(-1)">
        ⟨
      </button>
      <button class="absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 right-2 
             bg-black/50 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-full 
             hover:bg-black/70 transition z-10" onclick="changeSlide(1)">
        ⟩
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="py-15 md:py-20 max-[768px]:py-10" id="testimonials">
    <h2 id="testimonial" class="text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-8">
      Testimonials
    </h2>
    <div class="w-11/12 md:w-4/5 mx-auto overflow-hidden">
      <div class="flex transition-transform duration-500" id="sliderTrack">

        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="w-full flex-shrink-0 text-center px-2 md:px-4">
          <img src="images/ShamrockInternationalSchool.jpg"
            class="w-[300px] h-[180px] md:w-[470px] md:h-[300px] mx-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-3 md:mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">
            Shamrock International School (YIP 2023)
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-md mx-auto text-sm mt-1 md:mt-2">
            We thank the entire team of SBRC for the initiative and
            complying and managing everything in such difficult
            circumstances.
          </p>
          <p class="italic mt-2 md:mt-3">- Mrs AK Sindhu</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="w-full flex-shrink-0 text-center px-2 md:px-4">
          <img src="images/NHGoelSchool.jpeg.jpg"
            class="w-[300px] h-[180px] md:w-[470px] md:h-[300px] mx-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-3 md:mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">NH GOEL SCHOOL (YIP 2023)</h3>
          <p class="max-w-md mx-auto text-sm mt-1 md:mt-2">
            Big thanks to Team SBRC for hosting such a great event. We
            learned a lot, and your round-the-clock support was
            amazing. Thanks for being so hospitable. Here's to even
            more success in future YIPs!
          </p>
          <p class="italic mt-2 md:mt-3">- Mrs AK Sindhu</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="w-full flex-shrink-0 text-center px-2 md:px-4">
          <img src="images/AtomicEnergyCentralSchool.jpg"
            class="w-[300px] h-[180px] md:w-[470px] md:h-[300px] mx-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-3 md:mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">
            Atomic Energy Central School (YIP 2023)
          </h3>
          <p class="max-w-md mx-auto text-sm mt-1 md:mt-2">
            Thank you so much for all the help extended to us. It is
            indeed a life time memory for us. Thanks to everyone of
            SBRC team. We learnt a lot during our stay at IIT
            Kharagpur. Keep your spirits high. I can see a bright
            future in your eyes.
          </p>
          <p class="italic mt-2 md:mt-3">- Mrs AK Sindhu</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-gray-950 text-center text-gray-400">
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </footer>
  <script src="JS/home.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
